                              <SHORT-NAME>Frequency_Drift_Error</SHORT-NAME>
                              <DESC>
                                <L-2 L="EN">The ratio of the calibration pulse to the message length varies by greater than 1/64 or less than -1/64 from one message to another</L-2>
                              </DESC>
